              <tr><td><strong>Organic traffic</strong></td><td>Actual sessions from search</td><td>Business impact, traffic volume tracking</td><td>Affected by seasonality, GSC data gaps</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Keyword rankings</strong></td><td>Position for specific terms</td><td>Monitoring individual page performance</td><td>Volatile, misleading without volume weighting</td></tr>
